# TicketScout — Cloudflare Pages redirects
# NOTE: Subpath pages (concert, football, theatre, venue) are served as static HTML files
# from their respective folders. Do NOT add catch-all redirects for these paths.
# The rules below handle category landing pages and legacy redirects only.

# Category landing pages — serve the category HTML templates directly
/concerts   /concert.html   200
/football   /football.html  200
/theatre    /theatre.html   200

# Concert/football/theatre/venue subpaths — pass through to static files in those folders
# Cloudflare will serve e.g. /football/arsenal.html for /football/arsenal automatically.
# NO redirect rules needed here — omitting them lets the static files be found.
